    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 3. Incident Response\nMarine Environmental Scientist AI Agent writes the assessment, it is stored in the Incident Log, and authorities are emailed."
      },
      "id": "f657cba4-ae7a-461b-94df-cc6361b526e0",
